BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Chapter 1: Rethinking Weight Loss) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Why Most Diets Fail) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.2 Td (Research shows that 80-95% of diets fail long-term. This isn't because people lack) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.2 Td (willpower - it's because restrictive approaches are fundamentally unsustainable and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.2 Td (trigger biological compensation mechanisms.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 600.4 Td (The Diet Cycle) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.4 Td (- Restriction creates deprivation and cravings) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 570.4 Td (- Willpower inevitably breaks down) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.4 Td (- Overeating or binging occurs) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.4 Td (- Guilt and shame follow) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 528.4 Td (- More restriction is attempted) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 514.4 Td (- The cycle repeats with metabolic damage) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 484.6 Td (A Better Approach: Behavior Change) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 466.6 Td (- Focus on ADDING healthy behaviors, not restricting) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 452.6 Td (- Build habits that fit your life permanently) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 438.6 Td (- Aim for progress, not perfection) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 424.6 Td (- Address emotional eating patterns) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 410.6 Td (- Move your body from a place of respect, not punishment) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 396.6 Td (- Measure success beyond the scale) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 366.8 Td (Sustainable Weight Management Principles) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 348.8 Td (- No food is forbidden \(all foods fit\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 334.8 Td (- Eat enough - under-eating backfires) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 320.8 Td (- Protein and fiber at every meal) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 306.8 Td (- 80/20 approach - nourishing foods most of the time) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 292.8 Td (- Listen to hunger and fullness cues) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 278.8 Td (- Move in ways you enjoy) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 264.8 Td (- Prioritize sleep \(crucial for weight management\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 250.8 Td (- Manage stress \(cortisol promotes fat storage\)) Tj ET
endstream
