98 0 obj
<< /Length 2614 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Frequently Asked Questions) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Q: How fast should I expect to lose weight?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (Sustainable fat loss is 0.5-1 pound per week. Faster loss typically means muscle loss and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (is harder to maintain. Focus on trend over time, not day-to-day fluctuations.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 618.4 Td (Q: Should I count calories?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (Calorie counting works for some but triggers disordered eating in others. The plate) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (method, hunger/fullness awareness, and food quality focus work well without counting.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 560.6 Td (Q: What about cheat days?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.6 Td (The concept of 'cheating' implies restriction and guilt. Instead, practice flexible eating) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (- enjoy all foods without labeling them good or bad. No food is off-limits.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 502.8 Td (Q: Why did I stop losing weight \(plateau\)?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 486.8 Td (Plateaus are normal and expected. Your body adapts. Options: adjust portions slightly,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 472.8 Td (increase protein, add strength training, manage stress, or accept this as your body's set) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 458.8 Td (point.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 431.0 Td (Q: Is it possible to be healthy at a higher weight?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 415.0 Td (Health markers \(blood pressure, blood sugar, cholesterol, fitness level\) matter more than) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 401.0 Td (the number on the scale. Focus on behaviors and health outcomes.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 373.2 Td (Q: How do I handle emotional eating?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 357.2 Td (First, identify the emotion. Then ask: Am I physically hungry? If not, what do I actually) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 343.2 Td (need? \(Rest, connection, comfort, stimulation.\) Food is not the enemy, but it can't solve) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 329.2 Td (non-food problems.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 301.4 Td (Q: Does sleep really affect weight?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 285.4 Td (Absolutely. Poor sleep increases hunger hormones, decreases willpower, promotes fat) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 271.4 Td (storage, and makes you more likely to choose high-calorie foods. Prioritize 7-9 hours.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 243.6 Td (Q: How do I stay motivated long-term?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 227.6 Td (Motivation fades - habits sustain you. Focus on identity \('I am someone who moves daily'\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 213.6 Td (rather than goals. Track behaviors, not just outcomes. Celebrate non-scale wins.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
